text: hello good evening
Hi, very good evening! How do I help you?

Here are some which people often prefer with their families. What do you say about these?:yum:
Can you tell me the rating of the 3rd and 6th images
Great choice!!! the third image has 4.1/5:blush: rating by the customers and sixth one has 4.4/5 .
What are the specialties of the 6th one?
So what would you like to have there? :thinking_face:

Hey, they have multiple cuisines!! Let me show you some. Turkish, Spanish, Japanese, Italian, and last but not the least our very own Indian.:star-struck:

Have a look at this awesome food present in 4th cuisine.

Yeah sure. Let me get you some of those :slightly_smiling_face:

the best thing which goes with this is to have some drinks and cheese puffs:yum:

The outer crust is made out of whole wheat flour and inside you have some mashed potatoes :heart_eyes: with cheese in it. :slightly_smiling_face:

These are some varieties in non-vegetarian :wink:

Any further help do you want!!! like order or contact information or anything else?

your order is for how many people can you help me with that? Like how many pizzaz and drinks do you want. :slightly_smiling_face:
Just one of each
Then your total become 425/- Rs only :slightly_smiling_face:

Do you want to reorder or cancel some of the items from the list?

Then your total is 350 Rs. and you final order is

:slightly_smiling_face: Is there anything else I can help you with?

You are most welcome :slightly_smiling_face:
